pokedexEntries.diamond: When Burmy evolved, its cloak became a part of this Pokémon's body. The cloak is never shed.
pokedexEntries.pearl: Its appearance changes depending on where it evolved. The materials on hand become a part of its body.
pokedexEntries.platinum: When evolving, its body takes in surrounding materials. As a result, there are many body variations.
pokedexEntries.heartGold: It is said that a Wormadam that evolves on a cold day will have a thicker cloak.
